  nodes:
  - id: start
    speakerID: butler
    text: "\u266A Oh, mistress Vivienne\u2026 Your voice was more beautiful than
      the angels\u2019\u2026 \u266A"
    nextNodeID: start
    choices:
    - text: Excuse me?
      nextNodeID: 1
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      requiredReputation: 0
      reputationChange: 0
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    - text: See you
      nextNodeID: 
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      requiredReputation: 0
      reputationChange: 0
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 1
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 1
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Hm?\nOh\u2026 you\u2019re not her.\n\u2026Sorry."
    nextNodeID: 2
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 2
    speakerID: lyra
    text: "I\u2019m Lyra. I\u2019m trying to understand what happened to Vivienne."
    nextNodeID: 3
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 3
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Ah\u2026 my lady\u2026 Still radiant. Even now."
    nextNodeID: 4
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 4
    speakerID: lyra
    text: You cared about her a lot.
    nextNodeID: 5
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 1
  - id: 5
    speakerID: butler
    text: "More than anything. Well\u2026 perhaps equally to peanuts."
    nextNodeID: 6
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 6
    speakerID: butler
    text: But Lady Vivienne was allergic, so I learned restraint.
    nextNodeID: 7
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 7
    speakerID: lyra
    text: "You were there the night she died, weren\u2019t you?"
    nextNodeID: 8
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 8
    speakerID: butler
    text: Yes.
    nextNodeID: 9
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
  - id: 9
    speakerID: lyra
    text: What happened?
    nextNodeID: 10
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 10
    speakerID: butler
    text: "The manor was full of guests. A grand celebration, all for her final performance.
      She left during a short intermission before the last song\u2026 and never came
      back."
    nextNodeID: 11
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 11
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Laurent went looking for her first. Then\u2026 the screaming started."
    nextNodeID: 12
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 12
    speakerID: lyra
    text: Did you notice anything strange before that?
    nextNodeID: 13
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 13
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Lady Vivienne was frightened lately. She believed people around her wished
      her harm. \u2026But I would never let anything happen to her. "
    nextNodeID: 14
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 14
    speakerID: butler
    text: NEVER.
    nextNodeID: 
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
